summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Sixty-fourth Street from Eight Avenue N.W. to a point 300 feet west of the west margin of 15th Avenue N.W. in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 17703, creating Local Improvement District No. 1680 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
